Multivector division
The spacetime algebra is not a division algebra, because it contains idempotent elements 
  
    
      
        
          
            
              1
              2
            
          
        
        (
        1
        ±
        
          γ
          
            0
          
        
        
          γ
          
            i
          
        
        )
      
    
