The Dirac Equation
Spacetime algebra enables a description of the Dirac particle in terms of a real theory in place of a matrix theory. The matrix theory description of the Dirac particle is:

  
    
      
        
          
            
              
                γ
                ^
              
            
          
          
            μ
          
        
